nodes.text: Preigo's Traveling World of Wonder was an inter-galactic circus owned and directed by Preigo. The attraction often passed by Florrum where Hondo Ohnaka would request a show.

During one visit of Hondo's gang, the circus had been infiltrated by Jedi Initiates, who had come to rescue Ahsoka Tano from Hondo's custody. The show was ruined as the younglings caused a diversion, making the circus an unpopular show. Weequay pirates attacked the circus and the younglings, forcing Preigo to retreat inside the circus craft, leaving many of his acts behind in the process.
